

roscore                                                  **master** 

roslaunch robot_model robot_rviz.launch model:=robot.urdf  **rviz load **

rosrun rosserial_python serial_node.py /dev/ttyACM0        **start arduino**
rosrun rosserial_python serial_node.py /dev/ttyACM1        **start arduino**

rosrun joypkg JoyControl.py                              **start joystick**


sudo apt-get install ros-indigo-rosserial-arduino
sudo apt-get install ros-indigo-rosserial                 **to download ros_serial**

sudo apt-get install python-pygame                       **to download pygame**

